Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:36.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos me deixe executar você\N com minhas próprias mãos!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:44.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Semla...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:07.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Jorul!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...m...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...la!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Barbacascada-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Jorul-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se... m... la!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:45.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Segurem Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Apaguem o fogo da vila!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:49.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Peguem-na rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não sejam tão violentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:55.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você pode trazer semla?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:57.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há alguns no armazém \Npara o festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Traga-os, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,S-Sim!
