Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:12.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É perigoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:15.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se aproximem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gebur...
