Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:21.87,Principio,,0,0,0,,Fazendo uma entrega,\Ncruzando o mar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:25.95,Principio,,0,0,0,,Binks' Sake no porão\Nenquanto navegamos na brisa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.25,Principio,,0,0,0,,Longe onde os olhos podem ver,\No sol brilha alegremente
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.05,Principio,,0,0,0,,Enquanto os pássaros voam no céu\Ne cantam com alegria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.39,Principio,,0,0,0,,Enquanto os pássaros voam no céu\Ne cantam com alegria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:38.76,Principio,,0,0,0,,Diga adeus a todos,\Nadeus ao porto famoso
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:42.89,Principio,,0,0,0,,Navegando do anoitecer ao amanhecer\Ne cantando como um só
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:47.27,Principio,,0,0,0,,Cruzando ondas de ouro e prata,\Ntransformando-se em sprays de água
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:52.55,Principio,,0,0,0,,Navegando em nossa jornada\Naté os confins do mar!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.13,IS_ROM,hi-light,0,0,0,,{\an7\org(490.977,42.575)\pos(0.003,0.005)Kara Effector[fx] 3.4  Math kurisu: Jump Funny I [line origin: 8 - line fx: 106] \q2\fscx479.28\fscy55.75\t(0,83.42,\fscx479.28\fscy47.75)\t(83.42,920,\fscx479.28\fscy55.75)\p1}m 0 0 m 100 100 {\p0\r\t(0,460,\frz-30)\t(460,690,\fr0)\1c&HFF81EA&\t(0,460,\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFF81EA&\fscy136.5)\t(460,920,\1c&HFF81EA&\3c&H522601&\fscy105\bord1.8)}ri
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:37.09,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mas eu vou vendê-los ao Governo,\N não a piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um, dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um, dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:14:00.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Feliz aniversário, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:14:00.92,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Feliz aniversário, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:06.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:12.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Empilhamos sua comida favorita, semla,\N e fizemos este croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espero que esteja gostoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se chama croquembouche?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer uma festa do chá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma festa do chá?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:30.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Significa que vamos passar o tempo em uma mesa, bebendo chá e comendo doces!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer, vamos fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:33.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A festa do chá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:34.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sirvam o chá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vem, Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos começar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Come o quanto quiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:47.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bom apetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que delícia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Come super rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:03.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A festa do chá é divertida!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que felicidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que delícia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:13.29,Principio,,0,0,0,,Um dia, Mãe Carmel\N desapareceu repentinamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:19.38,Principio,,0,0,0,,Esse foi o melhor\N aniversário que Linlin teve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:29.09,Principio,,0,0,0,,Estar com seus amigos da Casa dos Cordeirinhos,\N que viveram o mesmo que ela...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:33.32,Principio,,0,0,0,,Mãe, gentil e generosa,\N a quem ela tanto amava.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:39.06,Principio,,0,0,0,,Ao se ver cercada pelos sorrisos de todos eles e comer seu doce, doce bolo de aniversário,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:43.23,Principio,,0,0,0,,Linlin não conseguiu parar de chorar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Come o quanto quiser, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:48.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou comer, vou comer tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:50.53,Principio,,0,0,0,,Que dia esplêndido.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:54.02,Principio,,0,0,0,,As lágrimas impediam-na\N de ver o que estava à sua frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:59.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, não se apresse, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fizemos isso para você!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,São todos para você!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Come mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos continuar sendo amigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos divertir juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que delícia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:25.91,Principio,,0,0,0,,Foi um aniversário esplêndido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lambeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, que feliz eu estou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:33.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu gostei tanto que\N sem querer mordi a mesa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:39.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca vou esquecer o que aconteceu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pessoal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mãe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.50,Principio,,0,0,0,,Um dia, Mãe Carmel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:56.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para onde foram?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.98,Principio,,0,0,0,,...desapareceu de repente.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:02.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein? Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:03.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde eles estão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estão em casa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:23.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, encontrei vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me deixem sozinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:52.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde vocês estão, pessoal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:04.84,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ei, Mãe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:09.22,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2200,0)}Por que você desapareceu de repente?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:27.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:28.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mamãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:35.05,Principio,,0,0,0,,Há sessenta e três anos, Mãe Carmel\N e várias crianças desapareceram.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:43.43,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2811)}Havia duas pessoas que observaram tudo o que aconteceu sem que Big Mom soubesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(528,0)}Onde eles estão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:53.26,Principio,,0,0,0,,Um era um guerreiro de Elbaf que apenas\N estava visitando a Casa dos Cordeirinhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:56.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-Ela é um monstro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:59.16,Principio,,0,0,0,,Ele ficou pálido e fugiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:02.94,Principio,,0,0,0,,E nunca mais voltou para aquela ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:10.48,Principio,,0,0,0,,Com o tempo, os gigantes de Elbaf e de todo o mundo souberam...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:15.64,Principio,,0,0,0,,...e Charlotte Linlin se tornou\N tão odiada...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:20.34,Principio,,0,0,0,,...que até seu nome se tornou\N uma palavra proibida.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para onde você foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:30.22,Principio,,0,0,0,,E a outra testemunha foi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:33.22,Principio,,0,0,0,,...Streusen, um cozinheiro\N que queria ser pirata,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:38.32,Principio,,0,0,0,,e que já vivia naquela ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:46.01,Principio,,0,0,0,,Ele achou o que aconteceu muito engraçado.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.74,Principio,,0,0,0,,Sua habilidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:09.26,Principio,,0,0,0,,...veio da fruta Kuku Kuku, que podia transformar qualquer objeto em comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:09.26,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,4620,5120)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.74,0:20:09.26,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,4620,5120)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:20:03.74,0:20:09.26,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,4620,5120)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:20:03.74,0:20:09.26,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,4620,5120)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:03.74,0:20:09.26,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,4620,5120)}Kuku vem de "cook", que significa cozinhar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:18.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca vi um\N monstro como ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:22.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me deixem sozinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:28.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1397}Será um desperdício se\N ela morrer por ficar sozinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para onde você foi, Mãe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:41.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que houve, garota?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:44.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chorar só vai te dar fome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:50.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que tal falarmos sobre sonhos, garota?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem é você, velho?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, não chegue muito perto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:57.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, velho, você viu a Mãe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sabe para onde todos foram?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não faço ideia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:03.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas com certeza voltarão logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:04.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, enquanto isso, eu vou te fazer companhia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sou bom em cozinhar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Posso te dar comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou com fome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:20.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viu só?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:49.07,Principio,,0,0,0,,Esses dois eventualmente se tornariam\N os fundadores dos Piratas da Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:09.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:11.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Recupere a compostura!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vão atirar em você!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:16.30,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}Por isso, se na festa do chá de hoje,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:21.77,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}quebrarmos esse retrato ao meio,\N o que você acha que vai acontecer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.60,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}Mamãe ficaria devastada!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:28.61,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}E ninguém poderá se mover\N por cinco segundos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:31.78,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}Lá, os mísseis KX\N funcionarão no máximo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:37.49,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}...e Big Mom, a Yonkou, morrerá!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:46.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Até aqui você chegou, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:49.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mamãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:09.92,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mãe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:13.28,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Todos ficam no meu caminho.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:23.91,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,A verdadeira felicidade para as pessoas\N é que todos sejam iguais.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.91,0:23:29.59,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Mas encontrar um país assim\N neste mundo é uma fantasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:34.12,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Então vamos fazer deste\N lugar um país!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:37.80,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Um país onde todos vejam\N as coisas da mesma maneira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:39.18,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Um país?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:39.18,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Um país?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:43.20,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sim, um país sem racismo\N ou discriminação...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:46.86,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,...e onde todos vejam as\N coisas da mesma maneira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:48.60,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ver as coisas da mesma maneira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:49.69,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Isso seria muito legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:54.09,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Todos deveriam ser maiores!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:57.00,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Ah, que incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:59.65,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É um grande sonho, Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:08.58,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:08.58,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.93,0:24:13.67,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vamos trabalhar juntos para conseguir isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.67,0:24:15.20,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vou me esforçar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:15.96,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Eu também!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:16.78,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,E eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:17.88,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:17.88,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.49,0:24:21.33,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Vamos construir um país dos sonhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:23.64,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Eu também vou me esforçar, Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.64,0:24:26.72,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Você é uma boa garota, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.72,0:24:28.60,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.60,0:24:33.95,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Se houvesse muitos países assim,\N o mundo seria mais pacífico.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.95,0:24:38.72,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Todos poderiam ser felizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.24,0:24:45.45,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,O sonho da Mãe era o meu sonho!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.26,0:24:47.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Paz?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.57,0:24:50.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse é o seu sonho, Linlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.09,0:24:52.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.01,0:24:56.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou construir um país que\N deixe a Mãe orgulhosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.32,0:25:13.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que tal parar de chorar agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.14,0:25:14.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.84,0:25:17.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quero ver a mágica da Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.24,0:25:18.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mágica?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.74,0:25:22.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, a Mãe era muito boa nisso.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.95,0:25:26.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela colocava as mãos assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.62,0:25:30.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E então...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.22,0:25:38.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor, flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.22,0:25:38.84,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor, flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.84,0:25:39.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.50,0:25:41.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A mágica que a Mãe fazia!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.68,0:25:42.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.70,0:25:44.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu também consegui!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.38,0:25:46.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.38,0:25:46.28,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.28,0:25:49.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor! Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.28,0:25:49.20,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor! Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.20,0:25:50.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Terra!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.85,0:25:53.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Terra!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.85,0:25:53.76,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:25:58.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.85,0:26:01.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma habilidade de Akuma no Mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.52,0:26:03.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.52,0:26:03.20,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.20,0:26:05.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Árvore, árvore!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.20,0:26:05.96,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.96,0:26:09.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.96,0:26:09.69,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.69,0:26:10.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.69,0:26:10.84,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.84,0:26:15.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.84,0:26:15.50,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Flor, flor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.50,0:26:16.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.84,0:26:18.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu também consegui, Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.93,0:26:21.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.93,0:26:21.02,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.02,0:26:23.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos cantar juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.02,0:26:23.70,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Vamos cantar juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.70,0:26:24.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Interessante!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.85,0:26:26.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem, já decidi!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.40,0:26:27.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou partir para o mar com ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.88,0:26:30.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Incrível, incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:31.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um país pacífico e igualitário...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.94,0:26:36.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...onde todos sejam grandes e possam ver as coisas da mesma maneira!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.36,0:26:43.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos construir esse país dos sonhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.01,0:26:45.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixe-me participar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.91,0:26:47.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.27,0:26:54.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, olhem este\N pôster de recompensa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.28,0:26:57.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cinquenta milhões de\N berries por uma garota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.74,0:27:02.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2446)}Como isso é possível?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.86,0:27:07.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma garota tomou\N conta de um castelo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.20,0:27:09.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A líder é Charlotte Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.50,0:27:13.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Cipher Pol informou que ela é perigosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:15.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela será uma grande vilã!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.12,0:27:16.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Capturem-na a qualquer custo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.98,0:27:18.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.98,0:27:18.55,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.94,0:27:24.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá está ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.44,0:27:28.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tenha cuidado, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.90,0:27:32.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou comendo doces!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.69,0:27:35.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não interrompam!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.98,0:27:49.24,Principio,,0,0,0,,Charlotte Linlin continuou\N causando destruição...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.24,0:27:55.45,Principio,,0,0,0,,...e rapidamente se tornou\N uma ameaça mundial.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.45,0:27:57.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.24,0:28:00.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.38,0:28:08.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me tragam doces!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.70,0:28:10.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sua Majestade!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.20,0:28:11.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que terrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.49,0:28:17.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se fizerem isso, prometo um\N país dos sonhos pacífico!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.38,0:28:22.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se me ouvirem, todos serão felizes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.74,0:28:29.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aqueles que não me ouvirem,\N terei que matá-los por egoísmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.34,0:28:33.00,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mãe, sinto sua falta...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.00,0:28:35.18,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Sinto sua falta!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.70,0:28:41.84,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.84,0:28:44.77,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Algum dia vou fazer todos grandes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.77,0:28:48.36,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Então vamos nos sentar\N todos em uma mesa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.98,0:28:54.62,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mas ainda há pessoas\N que não me escutam!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.99,0:29:01.45,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Estou tão triste\N que não paro de chorar!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.82,0:29:07.01,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Porque o único retrato da Mãe...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.86,0:29:09.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é uma boa garota.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.20,0:29:18.18,Pensante,,0,0,0,,O único retrato da Mãe\N que eu tanto valorizava...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.18,0:29:20.61,Pensante,,0,0,0,,...foi destruído!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.96,0:29:29.73,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Não vou perdoá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.11,0:29:34.03,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.91,0:29:52.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,5500)}Não vou perdoá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.98,0:30:20.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O plano falhou!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.21,0:30:26.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.20,0:30:31.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Falharam!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.76,0:30:39.43,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}Ouçam, como posso voar,\N aparecerei com um espelho para escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.43,0:30:45.30,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}Quando terminarmos, todos\N entraremos no espelho de Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.30,0:30:48.10,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente, é a minha vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.10,0:30:49.70,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.70,0:30:51.80,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ela destruiu meus mísseis!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.80,0:30:53.76,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Aquela velha monstruosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.76,0:30:56.17,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Afinal, ela é uma Yonkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.71,0:31:09.98,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Retirada, todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.98,0:31:11.89,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Pulem todos no espelho!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.24,0:31:34.15,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mas que pressão!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.19,0:32:19.24,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.24,0:32:20.74,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Estamos no telhado!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.74,0:32:22.20,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Não temos escapatória!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.05,0:32:27.87,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Nem chance de vitória!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.80,0:32:43.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rook In Voller Grösse!
